== Events == * {{ill|Kaō|ja|嘉応}} 2nd Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} {{ill|1170|ja|1170年}} {{ill|July 10|ja|7月10日}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara Hidetaka|ja|藤原秀衡}} of Ōshū was appointed as {{ill|Chinju-fu Shogun|ja|鎮守府将軍|lt=Chinju-fu Shogun}} by the Imperial Court. * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|正慶}} 2nd Year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} {{ill|1333|ja|1333年}} {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日}}) – {{ill|Emperor Kōgon|ja|光厳天皇|lt=Emperor Kōgon}} of the Northern Court abdicated in favor of {{ill|Emperor Godaigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|lt=Emperor Godaigo}} of the Southern Court, temporarily uniting the Nanboku-chō period. * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|正慶}} 5th Year / {{ill|Engei|ja|延元}} 1st Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} {{ill|1336|ja|1336年}} {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日}}) – The {{ill|Battle of Minatogawa|ja|湊川の戦い|lt=Battle of Minatogawa}}: {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|足利尊氏}} defeated {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成}}, who, along with his clan, committed suicide.
