== Deaths == * {{ill|Kōhō|ja|康保}} 4th Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} {{ill|967|ja|967年}} {{ill|July 5|ja|7月5日}}) – {{ill|Emperor Murakami|ja|村上天皇}}, the 62nd Emperor (born {{ill|926|ja|926年}}). * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|正慶}} 5th Year / {{ill|Engei|ja|延元}} 1st Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} {{ill|1336|ja|1336年}} {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日}}) – {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成}}, a military commander (born {{ill|1294|ja|1294年}}).
