[[cdo:5 nguŏk 25 hô̤ (nùng-lĭk)]] [[zh-min-nan:5 goe̍h 25 ji̍t (kū-le̍k)]] [[zh-yue:五月廿五]] {{Lunisolar May}} '''May 25''' is the 25th day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Kaō|ja|嘉応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1170|ja|1170th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 10|ja|7月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara Hidetaka|ja|藤原秀衡|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of Ōshū was appointed as {{ill|Chinju-fu Shogun|ja|鎮守府将軍|lt=Chinju-fu Shogun|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} by the Imperial Court. * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd Year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1333|ja|1333rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kōgon|ja|光厳天皇|lt=Emperor Kōgon|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of the Northern Court abdicated in favor of {{ill|Emperor Godaigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|lt=Emperor Godaigo|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of the Southern Court, temporarily uniting the Nanboku-chō period. * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th Year / {{ill|Engei|ja|Engen|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1336|ja|1336th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Battle of Minatogawa|ja|湊川の戦い|lt=Battle of Minatogawa|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} : {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} defeated {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , who, along with his clan, committed suicide.
== Births == * {{ill|Kakki|ja|Kakitsu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1442|ja|1442nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 3|ja|7月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Gotomimon|ja|後土御門天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 103rd Emperor (died {{ill|1500|ja|1500th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōō|ja|承応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1654|ja|1654th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 9|ja|7月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Reigen|ja|霊元天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 112th Emperor (died {{ill|1732|ja|1732nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenmei|ja|天明|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1782|ja|1782nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 5|ja|7月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Aizawa Shōshisai|ja|会沢正志斎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Confucian scholar of the Mito Domain (died {{ill|1863|ja|1863rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kōhō|ja|康保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|967|ja|967th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 5|ja|7月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Murakami|ja|村上天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 62nd Emperor (born {{ill|926|ja|926th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th Year / {{ill|Engei|ja|Engen|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1336|ja|1336th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a military commander (born {{ill|1294|ja|1294th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
