== Births == * {{ill|Kakki|ja|Kakitsu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1442|ja|1442nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 3|ja|7月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Gotomimon|ja|後土御門天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 103rd Emperor (died {{ill|1500|ja|1500th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōō|ja|承応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1654|ja|1654th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 9|ja|7月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Reigen|ja|霊元天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 112th Emperor (died {{ill|1732|ja|1732nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenmei|ja|天明|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1782|ja|1782nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 5|ja|7月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Aizawa Shōshisai|ja|会沢正志斎|1=Aizawa Seishisai|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Confucian scholar of the Mito Domain (died {{ill|1863|ja|1863rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kōhō|ja|康保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|967|ja|967th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 5|ja|7月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Murakami|ja|村上天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 62nd Emperor (born {{ill|926|ja|926th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th Year / {{ill|Engei|ja|Engen|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1336|ja|1336th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a military commander (born {{ill|1294|ja|1294th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
