{{Lunisolar May|qq=}} 
'''May 25''' is the 25th day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|12=draft}}  the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|qq=|12=draft}} . 
== Events ==
* {{ill|Kaō|ja|嘉応|qq=|12=draft}}  2nd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1170|ja|1170th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|July 10|ja|7月10日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara Hidetaka|ja|藤原秀衡|qq=|12=draft}}  of Ōshū was appointed as {{ill|Chinju-fu Shogun|ja|鎮守府将軍|lt=Chinju-fu Shogun|qq=|12=draft}}  by the Imperial Court.
* {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|qq=|12=draft}}  2nd Year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=|12=draft}}  3rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1333|ja|1333rd year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kōgon|ja|光厳天皇|lt=Emperor Kōgon|qq=|12=draft}}  of the Northern Court abdicated in favor of {{ill|Emperor Godaigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|lt=Emperor Godaigo|qq=|12=draft}}  of the Southern Court, temporarily uniting the Nanboku-chō period.
* {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|qq=|12=draft}}  5th Year / {{ill|Engei|ja|Engen|qq=|12=draft}}  1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1336|ja|1336th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Battle of Minatogawa|ja|湊川の戦い|lt=Battle of Minatogawa|qq=|12=draft}} : {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=|12=draft}}  defeated {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成|qq=|12=draft}} , who, along with his clan, committed suicide.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kakki|ja|Kakitsu|qq=|12=draft}}  2nd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1442|ja|1442nd year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|July 3|ja|7月3日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Gotomimon|ja|後土御門天皇|qq=|12=draft}} , the 103rd Emperor (died {{ill|1500|ja|1500th year|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Shōō|ja|承応|qq=|12=draft}}  3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1654|ja|1654th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|July 9|ja|7月9日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Reigen|ja|霊元天皇|qq=|12=draft}} , the 112th Emperor (died {{ill|1732|ja|1732nd year|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Tenmei|ja|天明|qq=|12=draft}}  2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1782|ja|1782nd year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|July 5|ja|7月5日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Aizawa Shōshisai|ja|会沢正志斎|1=Aizawa Seishisai|qq=|12=draft}} , a Confucian scholar of the Mito Domain (died {{ill|1863|ja|1863rd year|qq=|12=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Kōhō|ja|康保|qq=|12=draft}}  4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|967|ja|967th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|July 5|ja|7月5日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Murakami|ja|村上天皇|qq=|12=draft}} , the 62nd Emperor (born {{ill|926|ja|926th year|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|qq=|12=draft}}  5th Year / {{ill|Engei|ja|Engen|qq=|12=draft}}  1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1336|ja|1336th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成|qq=|12=draft}} , a military commander (born {{ill|1294|ja|1294th year|qq=|12=draft}} ).


