|lt=Chinju-fu Shogun|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chinju-fu Shogun|qq=}} by the Imperial Court. * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōkei|qq=}} 2nd Year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genkō|qq=}} 3rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1333|ja|1333rd year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1333|qq=}} {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 7|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kōgon|ja|光厳天皇|lt=Emperor Kōgon|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Kōgon|qq=}} of the Northern Court abdicated in favor of {{ill|Emperor Godaigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|lt=Emperor Godaigo|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Godaigo|qq=}} of the Southern Court, temporarily uniting the Nanboku-chō period. * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōkei|qq=}} 5th Year / {{ill|Engei|ja|Engen|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Engei|qq=}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1336|ja|1336th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1336|qq=}} {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 4|qq=}} ) – The {{ill|Battle of Minatogawa|ja|湊川の戦い|lt=Battle of Minatogawa|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Battle of Minatogawa|qq=}} : {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Takauji|qq=}} defeated {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kusunoki Masashige|qq=}} , who, along with his clan, committed suicide.
== Births == * {{ill|Kakki|ja|Kakitsu|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kakki|qq=}} 2nd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1442|ja|1442nd year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1442|qq=}} {{ill|July 3|ja|7月3日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 3|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Gotomimon|ja|後土御門天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Gotomimon|qq=}} , the 103rd Emperor (died {{ill|1500|ja|1500th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1500|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Shōō|ja|承応|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōō|qq=}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1654|ja|1654th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1654|qq=}} {{ill|July 9|ja|7月9日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 9|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Reigen|ja|霊元天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Reigen|qq=}} , the 112th Emperor (died {{ill|1732|ja|1732nd year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1732|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenmei|ja|天明|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenmei|qq=}} 2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1782|ja|1782nd year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1782|qq=}} {{ill|July 5|ja|7月5日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 5|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Aizawa Shōshisai|ja|会沢正志斎|1=Aizawa Seishisai|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Aizawa Shōshisai|13=User:Immanuelle/Aizawa Seishisai|qq=}} , a Confucian scholar of the Mito Domain (died {{ill|1863|ja|1863rd year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1863|qq=}} ).
