{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=五月廿五|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 5월 25일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 25''' is the 25th day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taian|qq=}} . == Events == * {{ill|Kaō|ja|嘉応|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaō|qq=}} 2nd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1170|ja|1170年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1170|qq=}} {{ill|July 10|ja|7月10日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 10|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara Hidetaka|ja|藤原秀衡|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujiwara Hidetaka|qq=}} of Ōshū was appointed as {{ill|Chinju-fu Shogun|ja|鎮守府将軍|lt=Chinju-fu Shogun|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chinju-fu Shogun|qq=}} by the Imperial Court. * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōkei|qq=}} 2nd Year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genkō|qq=}} 3rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1333|ja|1333rd year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1333|qq=}} {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 7|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kōgon|ja|光厳天皇|lt=Emperor Kōgon|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Kōgon|qq=}} of the Northern Court abdicated in favor of {{ill|Emperor Godaigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|lt=Emperor Godaigo|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Godaigo|qq=}} of the Southern Court, temporarily uniting the Nanboku-chō period. * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōkei|qq=}} 5th Year / {{ill|Engei|ja|Engen|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Engei|qq=}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1336|ja|1336年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1336|qq=}} {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 4|qq=}} ) – The {{ill|Battle of Minatogawa|ja|湊川の戦い|lt=Battle of Minatogawa|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Battle of Minatogawa|qq=}} : {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Takauji|qq=}} defeated {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kusunoki Masashige|qq=}} , who, along with his clan, committed suicide.
