inju-fu Shogun|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chinju-fu Shogun|qq=}} by the Imperial Court. * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōkei|qq=}} 2nd Year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genkō|qq=}} 3rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1333|ja|1333年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1333|qq=}} {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 7|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kōgon|ja|光厳天皇|lt=Emperor Kōgon|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Kōgon|qq=}} of the Northern Court abdicated in favor of {{ill|Emperor Godaigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|lt=Emperor Godaigo|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Godaigo|qq=}} of the Southern Court, temporarily uniting the Nanboku-chō period. * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōkei|qq=}} 5th Year / {{ill|Engei|ja|Engen|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Engei|qq=}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1336|ja|1336年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1336|qq=}} {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 4|qq=}} ) – The {{ill|Battle of Minatogawa|ja|湊川の戦い|lt=Battle of Minatogawa|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Battle of Minatogawa|qq=}} : {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Takauji|qq=}} defeated {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kusunoki Masashige|qq=}} , who, along with his clan, committed suicide.
