aft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1782|qq=}} {{ill|July 5|ja|7月5日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 5|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Aizawa Shōshisai|ja|会沢正志斎|1=Aizawa Seishisai|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Aizawa Shōshisai|13=User:Immanuelle/Aizawa Seishisai|qq=}} , a Confucian scholar of the Mito Domain (died {{ill|1863|ja|1863年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1863|qq=}} ).
