ment=jawiki link invalid}} 2nd Year / [[:en:Genkō (1331–1334)|Genkō]] 3rd Year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1333|1333]] [[:en:July 7|July 7]] ) – [[:en:Emperor Kōgon|Emperor Kōgon]] of the Northern Court abdicated in favor of [[:en:Emperor Go-Daigo|Emperor Godaigo]] of the Southern Court, temporarily uniting the Nanboku-chō period. * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōkei|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} 5th Year / {{ill|Engei|ja|Engen|1=Engen|2=ja|3=延元|qid=Q1194159|1=Engen|2=ja|3=延元|qid=Q1194159|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Engei|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1194159}} 1st Year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1336|1336]] [[:en:July 4|July 4]] ) – The [[:en:Battle of Minatogawa|Battle of Minatogawa]] : {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|1=Ashikaga Takauji|2=ja|3=足利尊氏|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|1=Ashikaga Takauji|2=ja|3=足利尊氏|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Takauji|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} defeated [[:en:Kusunoki Masashige|Kusunoki Masashige]] , who, along with his clan, committed suicide.
== Births == * {{ill|Kakki|ja|Kakitsu|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kakki|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} 2nd Year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1442|1442]] [[:en:July 3|July 3]] ) – [[:en:Emperor Go-Tsuchimikado|Emperor Gotomimon]] , the 103rd Emperor (died [[:en:1500|1500]] ). * [[:en:Jōō (Edo period)|Shōō]] 3rd Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1654|1654]] [[:en:July 9|July 9]] ) – [[:en:Emperor Reigen|Emperor Reigen]] , the 112th Emperor (died [[:en:1732|1732]] ). * [[:en:Tenmei|Tenmei]] 2nd Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1782|1782]] [[:en:July 5|July 5]] ) – [[:en:Aizawa Seishisai|Aizawa Seishisai]] , a Confucian scholar of the Mito Domain (died [[:en:1863|1863]] ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Kōhō|Kōhō]] 4th Year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:967|967]] [[:en:July 5|July 5]] ) – [[:en:Emperor Murakami|Emperor Murakami]] , the 62nd Emperor (born [[:en:926|926]] ). * {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōkei|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} 5th Year / {{ill|Engei|ja|Engen|1=Engen|2=ja|3=延元|qid=Q1194159|1=Engen|2=ja|3=延元|qid=Q1194159|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Engei|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1194159}} 1st Year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1336|1336]] [[:en:July 4|July 4]] ) – [[:en:Kusunoki Masashige|Kusunoki Masashige]] , a military commander (born [[:en:1294|1294]] ).
