'''May 25''' is the 25th day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May (Lunisolar)|qq=}}  the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Taian|qid=Q96759844|1=taian}}{{efn|ja|大安|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taian|1=taian|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q1306255}} . 
== Events ==
* {{ill|Kaō (era)|en|Kaō (era)|qid=Q1150842|lt=Kaō|1=Kaō (era)}}  2nd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}}  {{ill|1170|en|1170|qid=Q19681|lt=1170|1=1170}}  {{ill|July 10|en|July 10|qid=Q2689|lt=July 10|1=July 10}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Hidehira|en|Fujiwara no Hidehira|qid=Q3090625|lt=Fujiwara Hidetaka|1=Fujiwara no Hidehira}}  of Ōshū was appointed as {{ill|Chinjufu shōgun|en|Chinjufu shōgun|qid=Q2700052|lt=Chinju-fu Shogun|1=Chinjufu shōgun}}  by the Imperial Court.
* {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|1=Shōkyō|2=ja|3=正慶|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōkei|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q1069086}}  2nd Year / {{ill|Genkō (1331–1334)|en|Genkō (1331–1334)|qid=Q1194556|lt=Genkō|1=Genkō (1331–1334)}}  3rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}}  {{ill|1333|en|1333|qid=Q6004|lt=1333|1=1333}}  {{ill|July 7|en|July 7|qid=Q2694|lt=July 7|1=July 7}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kōgon|en|Emperor Kōgon|qid=Q471885|lt=Emperor Kōgon|1=Emperor Kōgon}}  of the Northern Court abdicated in favor of {{ill|Emperor Go-Daigo|en|Emperor Go-Daigo|qid=Q313942|lt=Emperor Godaigo|1=Emperor Go-Daigo}}  of the Southern Court, temporarily uniting the Nanboku-chō period.
* {{ill|Shōkei|ja|Shōkyō|1=Shōkyō|2=ja|3=正慶|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōkei|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q1069086}}  5th Year / {{ill|Engei|ja|Engen|1=Engen|2=ja|3=延元|qid=Q1194159|1=Engen|2=ja|3=延元|qid=Q1194159|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Engei|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q1194159}}  1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}}  {{ill|1336|en|1336|qid=Q6028|lt=1336|1=1336}}  {{ill|July 4|en|July 4|qid=Q2698|lt=July 4|1=July 4}} ) – The {{ill|Battle of Minatogawa|en|Battle of Minatogawa|qid=Q114620|lt=Battle of Minatogawa|1=Battle of Minatogawa}} : {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|1=Ashikaga Takauji|2=ja|3=足利尊氏|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|1=Ashikaga Takauji|2=ja|3=足利尊氏|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Takauji|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q297107}}  defeated {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|en|Kusunoki Masashige|qid=Q382234|lt=Kusunoki Masashige|1=Kusunoki Masashige}} , who, along with his clan, committed suicide.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kakki|ja|Kakitsu|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kakki|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}  2nd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}}  {{ill|1442|en|1442|qid=Q6411|lt=1442|1=1442}}  {{ill|July 3|en|July 3|qid=Q2699|lt=July 3|1=July 3}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Go-Tsuchimikado|en|Emperor Go-Tsuchimikado|qid=Q380623|lt=Emperor Gotomimon|1=Emperor Go-Tsuchimikado}} , the 103rd Emperor (died {{ill|1500|en|1500|qid=Q6126|lt=1500|1=1500}} ).
* {{ill|Jōō (Edo period)|en|Jōō (Edo period)|qid=Q1145081|lt=Shōō|1=Jōō (Edo period)}}  3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}}  {{ill|1654|en|1654|qid=Q6970|lt=1654|1=1654}}  {{ill|July 9|en|July 9|qid=Q2690|lt=July 9|1=July 9}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Reigen|en|Emperor Reigen|qid=Q313808|lt=Emperor Reigen|1=Emperor Reigen}} , the 112th Emperor (died {{ill|1732|en|1732|qid=Q6966|lt=1732|1=1732}} ).
* {{ill|Tenmei|en|Tenmei|qid=Q1194121|lt=Tenmei|1=Tenmei}}  2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}}  {{ill|1782|en|1782|qid=Q7740|lt=1782|1=1782}}  {{ill|July 5|en|July 5|qid=Q2696|lt=July 5|1=July 5}} ) – {{ill|Aizawa Seishisai|en|Aizawa Seishisai|qid=Q2090901|lt=Aizawa Seishisai|1=Aizawa Seishisai}} , a Confucian scholar of the Mito Domain (died {{ill|1863|en|1863|qid=Q7701|lt=1863|1=1863}} ).

== Deaths ==
